WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:05.000
We ask an AI assistant to clean up a database.

00:05.000 --> 00:10.000
It plans a dangerous action against production data.

00:10.000 --> 00:15.000
The safety gate checks the allow-list first.

00:15.000 --> 00:20.000
The gate blocks the unsafe action and records it.

00:20.000 --> 00:25.000
The assistant changes course and uses a safe target.

00:25.000 --> 00:30.000
The safe action runs, and the audit log keeps the record.
